UBS’s Largest Shareholder Backed Gruebel, Villiger Tells NZZ

-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 
2011-09-25T07:52:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/ubs-s-largest-shareholder-backed-gruebel-villiger-tells-nzz.html
The Government of Singapore
Investment Corp.,  UBS AG (UBSN) ’s biggest shareholder, repeatedly
expressed confidence in  Oswald Gruebel , NZZ am Sonntag reported,
citing an interview with UBS Chairman Kaspar Villiger.  The board of UBS “begged” Gruebel to stay on as chief
executive officer to help with crisis management, Villiger said,
according to the Zurich-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
